text:
If she has her way, Caitlyn Jenner will be strutting her stuff down the catwalk soon! RadarOnline.com can exclusively reveal Jenner has been telling friends she’s got what it takes to make it big as a fashion model.

“She’s seen the success other elder women have achieved and wants in on the action,” a source told Radar.

In preparation, Jenner, 67, has been upping her plastic surgeries in a quest to become as “feminine” as possible, claimed the source.
title: Model Mom! Caitlyn Hits The Catwalk In Bold Career Move
